# tallbox
## Company blurb

We are an Interior & Architectural Visualization studio with representatives in London and Chester / Cheshire with a dedicated management project system that ensures the quality of the work.

Learn more about us at https://www.tallboxdesign.com

## Company size

Approximately 5+ employees split between our SF offices and many remote employees across the globe.

## Remote status

Remote friendly!

You're expected to maintain a regular day-to-day schedule and be in the 'office' & responsive during your chosen work time.  
That said, we offer lots of flexibility for adjusting your schedule based on personal/family needs. 



## Office locations

London, Chester

